Halfway through the first round, Zhang connected with a short lead elbow to drop Diaz, and followed up with heavy ground strikes to earn his second first-round finish in as many UFC fights.
assets.event: UFC Fight Night: Yan vs Figueiredo

assets.name: JESUS AGUILAR | UFC 290
assets.description: Following a submission loss in his UFC debut, Dana White's Contender Series alum, Jesus Aguilar, faced Shannon The Turkish Delight Ross at UFC 290. In what became the second-fastest flyweight finish to date. Aguilar landed a massive overhand right that knocked Ross out cold in a stunning KO performance.

assets.name: DANIEL RODRIGUEZ | UFC FIGHT NIGHT FEB 15, 2020
assets.description: Making his UFC debut on short notice, Daniel Rodriguez stepped up against veteran Tim Means at UFC Fight Night: Anderson vs Blachowicz 2. After rocking Means on the feet, Rodriguez sealed the upset with a second-round guillotine choke to earn the Performance of the Night bonus.
assets.event: UFC Fight Night: Anderson vs Blachowicz 2

assets.name: DIONE BARBOSA | UFC FIGHT NIGHT APR 05, 2025
assets.description: Making her third UFC appearance, Dione The Witch Barbosa squared off against veteran flyweight Diana Belbita at UFC Fight Night: Emmett vs Murphy. The Brazilian grappling specialist made quick work of the bout, locking in an arm-triangle choke late in round one to earn a bounce-back victory.
assets.event: UFC Fight Night: Emmett vs Murphy

assets.name: JOE PYFER | UFC 287
assets.description: Finishing one of the most prolific middleweight submission artists in the UFC on his way up the ranks, Joe Bodybagz Pyfer pushed Gerald Meerschaert against the fence and landed a massive left hook to floor the veteran before following up with ground and pound to finish.
assets.event: UFC 287

assets.description: Representing Brazil and Team Grasso, Mairon Santos Alves faced fellow TUF teammate Kaan Ofli in the featherweight final for Season 32.
